name: WittyInsults
0:
”Alexa, ask Witty Insults to insult me.”
”Bless me with an insult.”
”Insult us.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: witty insults
des: This app was created with the intention of getting laughs from all parties involved and is by no means promoting bullying of any kind. Basically, this app was made to hurl fun insults at anyone that Alexa is asked to insult and was created with only good intentions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
